quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  13,35,"Imiterere y’ijuru ryasezeranyijwe abagandukira (Allah), ni iritembamo imigezi, imbuto zaryo zihoraho ndetse n’igicucu cyaryo (gihoraho). Iryo (juru) ni ryo herezo ry’abagandukira (Allah), naho iherezo ry’abahakanye ni umuriro.",""
  13,36,"Kandi ba bandi twahaye ibitabo (abaje kwemera muri bo) bishimira ibyo wahishuriwe (Qur’an, kuko ihuje n’ibyo bafite mu bitabo byabo), ariko hari n’udutsiko muri bo duhakana bimwe muri byo. Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Mu by’ukuri nategetswe kugaragira Allah (wenyine) no kutagira ibyo mubangikanya na byo. Nanahamagarira (abantu) kumugana, kandi iwe ni ho garukiro ryanjye.”",""
  13,37,"(Nk’uko twahishuriye ibitabo Intumwa zakubanjirije biri mu ndimi zazo), ni na ko twayiguhishuriye (Qur’an) ari amategeko (yo kuyoboresha) iri mu (rurimi rw’) Icyarabu, kugira ngo uyiyoboreshe. Kandi nuramuka ukurikiye amarangamutima yabo (ababangikanyamana) nyuma y’uko ugezweho n’ubumenyi, nta nshuti cyangwa umutabazi uzagira wo kukurinda (ibihano) bya Allah.",""
  13,38,"Kandi rwose twohereje Intumwa mbere yawe (yewe Muhamadi), tunazigenera (gushaka) abagore (no kugira) urubyaro. Ndetse nta Ntumwa yazana igitangaza bidaturutse ku bushake bwa Allah. Buri kintu cyose gifite igihe cyagenewe.",""
  13,39,"Allah ahanagura cyangwa akemeza ibyo ashaka (mu mategeko ye). Kandi ni We ufite igitabo gihatse ibindi [(Al Lawuh-ul Mahfudh) (urubaho rurinzwe)].",""
  13,40,"N’iyo twakwereka (yewe Muhamadi) bimwe mu byo tubasezeranya (ibihano) cyangwa tukakuzuriza igihe cyawe (ugapfa), mu by’ukuri inshingano zawe ni ugusohoza ubutumwa, maze ibarura rikaba iryacu.",""
  13,41,"Ese ntibabona ko mu by’ukuri dusenya ubutaka tukagenda tubugabanya mu mpande zabwo zose? Allah ni We utegeka kandi nta wavuguruza itegeko rye, ndetse ni We ubanguka mu ibarura.",""
  13,42,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi babayeho mbere yabo bacuriye imigambi mibisha (Intumwa zabo), ariko Allah ni We uburizamo imigambi mibisha yose. Azi neza ibyo buri muntu akora, kandi abahakanyi bazamenya uzagira iherezo ryiza.",""
